question: Find 3 characters with fastrf_embedding values where the first element is greater than 0.5.
cypher:
MATCH (c:Character)
WHERE c.fastrf_embedding[0] > 0.5
RETURN c.name, c.fastrf_embedding
LIMIT 3

question: Identify the characters in the top 10% of pagerank values.
cypher:
// First, find the threshold for the top 10% of pagerank values
MATCH (c:Character)
WITH percentileCont(c.pagerank, 0.9) AS top10PercentThreshold

// Then, find the characters with pagerank values in the top 10%
MATCH (c:Character)
WHERE c.pagerank >= top10PercentThreshold
RETURN c.name, c.pagerank
ORDER BY c.pagerank DESC
error: TypeQL has no percentileCont or percentile aggregation function. Cannot compute dynamic statistical thresholds.
